data.description: Quaint 3 bedroom 1 bathroom home located in the heart of Alamogordo. Home includes refrigerated air, a spacious backyard and an updated interior. Fresh stucco look with easy maintenance. Newer windows, new water heater, and a mini split system located in the third bedroom. Bathroom includes a spacious tiled shower. Sits perfectly within minutes of any town amenities you may need!
